{"tid":1564467,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"放學咪撚再跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T11:33:53.000Z","uid":173513,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c1664e7508279b77bc704243a84e03b5a97eb05c","tid":1564467,"uid":173513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:59:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於放學或者轉場，我想講，大家可唔可以唔好再用黨鐵？721、831黨鐵一再出賣大家，其實已經毫無懸念，黨鐵係絕對唔會保障乘客安全！但每一次，大家都係要逼去搭，唔係俾唔俾鐵嘅問題，係唔知幾時會有狗突然衝上車打人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵缺點：<br />\n1. 車站位於地底，容易掩飾真相，831大家都已經見識到<br />\n2. 車站只有固定數量嘅出口，一旦有狗，只可以困獸鬥<br />\n3. Cctv眾多，位置隱蔽，換校服唔方便，而且大家需要時，只有截圖</span><br />\n<br />\n建議大家逃生時搭巴士<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">巴士優點：<br />\n1. 地面行走，全車滿佈玻璃窗，車上唔俾影，周圍都可以影住狗嘅一舉一動<br />\n2. 巴士站冇固定出入口，隨意be water<br />\n3. 車上cctv有固定位置，可以輕易遮蔽方便換校服</span><br />\n<br />\n大家之後幾日唔好再咁傻，太子沉冤未雪，我哋一個都不能少。求祈上一架巴士再揾路返屋企，好過落黨鐵送頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e2fdd7af60e19b640462fad836d351fa60754ea7","tid":1564467,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:59:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2c0f3240f2b2e5c028e6fb46e9afbe495344d605","tid":1564467,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"和理非式搭鐵三寶：<br />\n1.正常八達通<br />\n2.綠卡<br />\n3.隨身已入閘單程飛一張<br />\n<br />\n情境一：<br />\n已入閘時查飛，show 單程飛<br />\n<br />\n情境二：<br />\n出閘時查飛，show正常八達通<br />\n<br />\n情境三：<br />\n查到無效飛，無賴扮唔知/補飛/罰錢/9秒9"},{"pid":"86f707a49e17589197835b04c415ccb0de12425a","tid":1564467,"uid":312670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"跳唔跳閘自己諗，但要清楚現時風險<br />\n狗而家用入侵罪告，可能留案底，並用大量狗睇閘<br />\n我就覺得唔值得搏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/739313369853225/posts/775945316190030?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F739313369853225%2Fposts%2F775945316190030%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmCpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=aca2f5b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/739313369853225/posts/775945316190030?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"3d3118a9a76153ab813ea00abc7a571da64dab6d","tid":1564467,"uid":173513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"86f707a49e17589197835b04c415ccb0de12425a","tid":1564467,"uid":312670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"跳唔跳閘自己諗，但要清楚現時風險<br />\n狗而家用入侵罪告，可能留案底，並用大量狗睇閘<br />\n我就覺得唔值得搏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/739313369853225/posts/775945316190030?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F739313369853225%2Fposts%2F775945316190030%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmCpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=aca2f5b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/739313369853225/posts/775945316190030?sfns=mo</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef29e59e10af515d5773b19dcfe4d880f1de7d0b","tid":1564467,"uid":173513,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"講緊手足散水放學